</strong><br /> <strong>“死亡天使”</strong> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="SLAYER - Raining Blood + Black Magic - 芝加哥防暴节现场 - 22/9/2024" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WJlPDGfczlA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="SLAYER - 简介 + South of Heaven - 芝加哥 Riot Fest 现场直播 - 2024 年 9 月 22 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ip7SgD5ZfMo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Slayer - 仇恨世界（Live Riot Fest Chicago 2024）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LriESYflruw?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Slayer - 213 - Riot Fest 2024 芝加哥" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dVvTyEDJ2f8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在克里·金 (Kerry King) 在公布复出表演几周前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slayers-kerry-king-announces-solo-album-from-hell-i-rise-3582796">宣布推出个人专辑</a>后，Slayer 重聚的机会似乎渺茫。这位音乐家此前曾将这个新项目描述为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kerry-king-says-new-project-extention-of-slayer-3570699">“Slayer 的延伸”。</a></p><p> “没有什么能比得上我们在舞台上现场表演的 90 分钟，与我们的粉丝分享强烈的能量，”汤姆·阿拉亚 (Tom Araya) 在一份关于他们的音乐节演出的声明中说道（来自<a href